			<div class="inner">
				<h2>What we do</h2>
				<p>RealWorld makes the transition from college to the real world easy</p>
				<div class="features">
					<section>
						<span class="icon major fa-code"></span>
						<h3>Rooming</h3>
						<p>RealWorld walks you through every step of moving into a new place, from apartment hunting to the house warming party</p>
